{
  "texts": [
    "Species composition of metagenomes was determined by MetaPhlAn4.",
    "A Beta diversity expressed as Aitchison distances in a principal component analysis (PCA).",
    "Percentages on the X-and Y-axis represent the variance explained by the first two components.",
    "B Aitchison distance from patient species profile to corresponding donor.",
    "C-E Species richness, Shannon index and Simpson evenness compared between donors and recipients, respectively."
